description:
Support us on Patreon: http://www.patreon.com/littlelightstudios/

Most people want to go to the good place!  Find out how the good place is being portrayed on television and how Hollywood plays with Biblical themes and characters in a way that will have you all mixed up.  


Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/littlelightstudios
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/littlelightstudios/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/llightstudios
SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/littlelightstudios

This is the gear we use to make and produce our videos:
Main Camera: Sony a7S II
